    316          /**
    317           * Assign water status according to filtered wash pump current, power or phase shift value.
    318           *
    319           * Call rate is 25ms.
    320           * It is possible to detect which motor is connected by measuring current and phase shift.
    321           * If phase shift is higher than phase shift threshold (150) or if phase shift is below threshold and current
    322           * is below current threshold (60), smart motor is connected. This check should be done in calibration state.
    323           */

